ria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Sept 08, 2023</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104cxv1693905302584.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/cxv1693905302584.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/cxv1693905302584.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"cxv1693905302584\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">You can uppercase and lowercase code in the Uniface IDE using the IDE code editor popup\n\t\tmenu.</p>\n<p class=\"p\">You need to right-click and click <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Uppercase</span> on the popup menu to\n\t\t\tuppercase the current selection. Similarly, you need to right-click inside a selection\n\t\t\tand click <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Lowercase</span> to lowercase a selected text. You can always\n\t\t\tundo uppercase and lowercase actions with <kbd class=\"ph userinput\">Ctrl+Z</kbd>.</p>\n<p class=\"p\">Additionally, you can use the default shortcut keys defined for\n\t\t\t\t<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Uppercase</span> and <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Lowercase</span> feature in the\n\t\t\t\t<span class=\"ph filepath\">[userkeys]</span> section of the <span class=\"ph filepath\">usys.ini</span> file.\n\t\t\tThe default shortcut keys defined in the <span class=\"ph filepath\">usys.ini</span> file are\n\t\t\t\t<kbd class=\"ph userinput\">Ctrl+U</kbd> to uppercase a selection and\n\t\t\t\t<kbd class=\"ph userinput\">Ctrl+Shift+U</kbd> to lowercase a selected code as defined in the\n\t\t\tfollowing block.</p>\n<div class=\"p\">\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104cxv1693905302584_html_0\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"cxv1693905302584__codeblock_nzh_zl4_ryb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">[USERKEYS]\ncode.uppercase=Ctrl+U\ncode.lowercase=Ctrl+Shift+U</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n<p class=\"p\"><strong class=\"ph b\">Limitation</strong></p>\n<p class=\"p\">The <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Uppercase</span> and <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Lowercase</span> functions do not work\n\t\t\tif a selection spans over the declarations section or other sections denoted by their\n\t\t\tnames. These functions only works when a selected code is inside the area defined in the\n\t\t\tcode editor. If you cannot change the case of a selection, the editor will display a\n\t\t\tmessage popup.</p>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_4714014\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_4714014\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Uppercase and lowercase code Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Sept 08, 2023 Summarize Uniface 10.4 You can uppercase and lowercase code in the Uniface IDE using the IDE code editor popup menu. You need to right-click and click Uppercase on the popup menu to uppercase the current selection. Similarly, you need to right-click inside a selection and click Lowercase to lowercase a selected text. You can always undo uppercase and lowercase actions with Ctrl+Z . Additionally, you can use the default shortcut keys defined for Uppercase and Lowercase feature in the [userkeys] section of the usys.ini file. The default shortcut keys defined in the usys.ini file are Ctrl+U to uppercase a selection and Ctrl+Shift+U to lowercase a selected code as defined in the following block. Explain this code [USERKEYS] code.uppercase=Ctrl+U code.lowercase=Ctrl+Shift+U Copy Limitation The Uppercase and Lowercase functions do not work if a selection spans over the declarations section or other sections denoted by their names. These functions only works when a selected code is inside the area defined in the code editor. If you cannot change the case of a selection, the editor will display a message popup. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}